{"tid":1865673,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"網購口罩集運討論 3","createTime":"2020-02-06T10:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T02:23:03.000Z","uid":3233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d10c7f1ab4ca66aa10baca0b4bb56332d9198312","tid":1865673,"uid":3233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>內容及資料僅供參考，投資涉及風險，口罩價格可升亦可跌，甚至變成亳無價值。投資者在決定是否購買有關口罩之前應先閱讀有關風險評估，以了解該建議發售之詳細資料，並應就本身的財務、其他狀況及需要，詳細考慮並決定購買有關口罩是否切合本身特定的需要，若有需要更應咨詢其他專業意見，方可作出有關購買決定。<br />\n忠告：親自買罩 咪俾錢炒狗</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間間集運都爆，唔好再問邊間快啲邊間好用，根本就無人知。記得留意返集運公司對體積重收費同要求，隨時運費貴過口罩本身，重有拒收嘅風險存在。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon自己送<br />\nKatolec=老人<br />\nYamato=貓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>麻煩大家Amazon唔好再用殘體字 有得揀英文/日文</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsq6yyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzsq6yyZ.jpg&h=8752b55a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eff066a87230c8a97501a41a2bf4c7e4a29935","tid":1865673,"uid":23977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0232953d338f463c23d83db9cb44b8049f41d506","tid":1865673,"uid":236227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:08:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1